  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こ、これは？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A-and who this might be...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46972</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やーやーやー、どもども。
『&lt;Suzu&gt;ちん』はじめましてだど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Greetings fellow people! The great Albert is here! Nice to meet you, Lil' &lt;Suzu&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47040</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>は、はじめまして</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>D-delighted to make your acquaintance.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いんやー、&lt;Suzu&gt;ちんは&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;に劣らず
かわいいだな。すんばらしいだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Maaan with the exception of &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; YOU are the cutest thing alive, Lil' &lt;Suzu&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……そんなこと突然、言われても困ります</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Please refrain from making such rash comments.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>えーだ、えーだ。その照れてる顔もグッとくるだどー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ahh that reserved shy smile only feels right in a delicate bird like you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>アルベルトさん、
新しい女の人が来るたび同じこと言ってませんか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mister Albert, do you need to say the exact same thing to every woman that joins our travels?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47624</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おんやー、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;、嫉妬だべかぁ～？
嫉妬かぁ？　いんや、モテる男は辛いだーな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;! Ain't any need to get jealous now! You're both fighting over me? Man, I'm such a stud I didn't notice!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んなもん、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;が一番に決まってるだーよ。
だども、&lt;Suzu&gt;ちんのあの恥じらい、捨てがてなぁ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How difficult... &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; is the cutest...but Lil' &lt;Suzu&gt;'s shyness is making me go crazy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうすっかなぁ。あっちもいいけどこっちもええな。
贅沢な悩みだーな。ぶつぶつ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What to do...? There's no shortage of good options but a man's gotta decide... Or maybe I could go with both...Hehehehehe...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48012</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あまり、気にしないでね。いつも、あんな感じだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Err, just ignore him for now. He'll go back to normal in a while.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48076</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_064_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>は、はい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-I shall.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
